title: Hey Big Trender 2/20: Kurt Cobain, Hanau, Fortnite, Arsenal
itunes:title: Hey Big Trender 2/20: Kurt Cobain, Hanau, Fortnite, Arsenal
description:
On this edition of Hey Big Trender Miles and DJ Danl discuss Kurt Cobain's birthday (he would have been 53), a right-wing terrorist attack in Hanau, Germany, Fortnite Season 2 has begun, and Arsenal squeezes out a late game victory against Olympiacos.
